<FIRST>u i AM-Dollar-Yen 1stLd-Writethru   08-16 0033</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Dollar-Yen, 1st Ld-Writethru,a0711,0031</SECOND>
<HEAD>Eds: CORRECTS opening dollar figure</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The dollar opened at 142.25 yen on the Tokyo foreign
exchange market Thursday, up from Wednesday's close of 141.80 yen.
</TEXT>
