higher an hour earlier after bouncing off 2,700 early in the day.
   Advancing issues outpaced declines by about 11 to 8 on the New
York Stock Exchange, with 826 issues up, 603 down and 519 unchanged.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 125.45 million shares.
